ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Whether this practitioner role record is in active use.

ivardefs.name: availabilityExceptions
ivardefs.desc: A description of site availability exceptions, e.g. public holiday availability. Succinctly describing all possible exceptions to normal site availability as details in the available Times and not available Times.

ivardefs.name: availableTime_
ivardefs.desc: A collection of times the practitioner is available or performing this role at the location and/or healthcareservice.

ivardefs.name: code_
ivardefs.desc: Roles which this practitioner is authorized to perform for the organization.

ivardefs.name: endpoint_
ivardefs.desc: Technical endpoints providing access to services operated for the practitioner with this role.

ivardefs.name: healthcareService_
ivardefs.desc: The list of healthcare services that this worker provides for this role's Organization/Location(s).

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Business Identifiers that are specific to a role/location.

ivardefs.name: location_
ivardefs.desc: The location(s) at which this practitioner provides care.

ivardefs.name: notAvailable_
ivardefs.desc: The practitioner is not available or performing this role during this period of time due to the provided reason.

ivardefs.name: organization
ivardefs.desc: The organization where the Practitioner performs the roles associated.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period during which the person is authorized to act as a practitioner in these role(s) for the organization.

ivardefs.name: practitioner
ivardefs.desc: Practitioner that is able to provide the defined services for the organization.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details that are specific to the role/location/service.

properties.desc: A specific set of Roles/Locations/specialties/services that a practitioner may perform at an organization for a period of time.
